{"tid":519302,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"7隻蛆住在她的手臂裡　雙夾抓蛆很療癒","createTime":"2018-01-04T08:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T18:53:54.000Z","uid":1221,"like":72,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"b8313c862250a39699dea5bec96e4e4b303908b9","tid":519302,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"嚇人！國外一名年輕女子之前到中南美洲進行生態工作，結果被膚蠅產卵寄生在她的手臂裡，接受治療時竟然從左臂夾出了7隻蛆。<br />\n醫師Guy Sterne將夾蛆影片po到《YouTube》，醫師左右手各拿一支夾子將女子抓蛆，女子則顯得淡定，還能和醫師聊天，但看到肥蛆從手臂裡被夾出時，仍然忍不出驚呼出聲。<br />\nGuy Sterne表示，女子在進行生態工作時多次被叮咬，這次總共夾出了7隻蛆。網友則似乎把夾蛆當成擠痘痘來欣賞，覺得看蛆被夾出手臂那一刻，感覺真是很舒爽、很療癒。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5Iyjnk5ZOfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5Iyjnk5ZOfE&d=JSzv5puKCyEP%2Bw%2Ffh5mnCUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=bfbfd27d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5Iyjnk5ZOfE</a>"},{"pid":"6604bfcea56688780663fde38d4ea667a6cfc200","tid":519302,"uid":157128,"like":109,"dislike":1,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:23:13.000Z","msg":"肥蛆<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63eb13666c5e4786e942cf733307c9d2a7192296","tid":519302,"uid":53568,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69683a4db1d9495c7865ec07dce3b68fc54b5b79","tid":519302,"uid":2035,"like":72,"dislike":1,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T08:44:39.000Z","msg":"條片得5條<br />\n<br />\n如果粗魯得濟斷係入面都唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb809317a025a40d8c2b261026ed21098adcb31","tid":519302,"uid":102179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s